Yankee Realty Corporation v. North Haven Lanes, Inc., et al. (12577)

O’Connell, Laveey and Heiman, Js.

Argued November 29 decision released December 20, 1994 *932Kevin P. Walsh, with whom, on the brief, was Michael F. O’Connor, for the appellant (plaintiff). Edward Wood Dunham, with whom, on the brief, was Eleanor S. DeVane, for the appellees (defendant Joseph R. Greco et al.). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
